{"tid":2401583,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗財困夫婦墮樓亡　兒子疑打退堂鼓涉唆使被帶署調查","createTime":"2021-02-10T00:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T05:44:59.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7d74fa38c877e22c14e068e6b313b11bd7b907ff","tid":2401583,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T00:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/52c2f84ec058cb9b97866c36f77aea43/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210210/_2021021007103655538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F52c2f84ec058cb9b97866c36f77aea43%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210210%2F_2021021007103655538.jpg&h=56518e90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n元朗財困夫婦墮樓亡，兒子疑打退堂鼓涉唆使被帶署調查。<br />\n<br />\n元朗一對夫婦凌晨1時許懷疑從安興街50號好彩洋樓高處飛墮平台，插穿一間僭建屋頂部的簷篷墮地，昏迷不醒，街坊發現報警，消防員趕至協助將女子抬下送院搶救，惟男子已證實死亡，女子送往博愛醫院搶救不治。兩死者年齡逾60歲，警員隨即封鎖現場調查男女墮樓原因，警員尋獲死者兒子，將他帶返警署調查。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，一家三口因財務問題決議尋死，惟兒子最後關頭打消念頭，不排除有人涉及唆使他人自殺等行為。現場消息指，死者懷疑因欠債問題輕生，事前曾發訊息通知友人，其友人立刻報警，稍後即有街坊發現兩人墮樓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/f5ff29f0e85774e488eb92e4641da96a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210210/_2021021007103780129.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2Ff5ff29f0e85774e488eb92e4641da96a%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210210%2F_2021021007103780129.jpg&h=50210709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/1bdd5e324738b0f14c87b07e39d6055f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210210/_2021021007103218319.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F1bdd5e324738b0f14c87b07e39d6055f%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210210%2F_2021021007103218319.jpg&h=f5283c17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/a50fbca691d28d02aa87611a511b655f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210210/_20